race.description: Bet365 Same Race Multi Maiden Plate
race.comment: BORN SURVIVOR (1) improved again last start beaten just half a length over 1600m at Cranbourne. Suitably placed and just has to hold that level of form to go one better. BERTRAND (7) is a threat. Looked good in his jumpouts before placing second at Stawell on debut behind Russian Choice. He's a promising type in good hands with plenty of improvement to come. The step up to a mile shouldn't be a bother. LICENTIOUS (9) was quickly back on track beaten 1.3L at Yarra Valley over 1500m. Peaks for this and is a chance to get the prise. WAVENDON (4) turned in a nice run second-up, finding a place over 1429m at Werribee after being in contention on the turn. Fitter again and is well in the mix.
